%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false, 'flowchart': {'htmlLabels': false}}}%%
flowchart TD
  Update["Consent write via API\ncreate / update / withdraw / migrate"]
  Tx[("PostgreSQL Tx:\nconsent_records + consent_audit")]
  Update --> Tx
  Tx --> Hot
  subgraph Storage[Storage lifecycle]
    direction LR
    Hot[("Hot partitions\n0–12 months")] -->|nightly ETL| Warm[("S3 Standard-IA\n12–24 months")]
    Warm -->|lifecycle policy| Cold[("S3 Glacier\n2–5 years")]
    Cold -->|retention expiry| Erase["Crypto-erase\nor delete"]
  end
  Hot --> Query["DSAR / regulator audit query"]
  Warm --> Query
  Cold -.restore.-> Query
